metadata.name: Cleopatra
metadata.description:
This photo attracts us with colours and a sense of relief. You feel the energy of zeroing, rejuvenation and shedding of the second skin. Especially after a hard and long day at work. I find a hot bath one of the most organic and natural process of zeroing in our time.  This photo is a reminder to us about ourselves, about our needs and about our competent distribution of resources. We should not forget to relax from time to time.

Artist: Pornsoup
